Here we go.

00:45:31.000 --> 00:45:33.899
Well, I live in--
I'm from Scripps.

00:45:33.899 --> 00:45:35.440
This is what it
looks like every day.

00:45:35.440 --> 00:45:37.212
So up here, I have
to put on a jacket.

00:45:39.935 --> 00:45:44.010
I thought I would go ahead and
put my cartoon, my favorite one

00:45:44.010 --> 00:45:46.220
out in front,
because we've lived

00:45:46.220 --> 00:45:48.560
in kind of a politicized
environment the last two years

00:45:48.560 --> 00:45:49.490
as climate scientists.

00:45:49.490 --> 00:45:51.281
And I think it's
